c Integer-weighted model counting (--weight-type integer path).
c All weights are integers so the mpz parser is exercised; the rational
c path never reaches it. Clause (x1 v x2) has 3 models; the weighted sum is
c   x1 x2 : 2*5 = 10
c   x1 ~x2: 2*7 = 14
c  ~x1 x2 : 3*5 = 15
c  total  = 39
c p weight 1 2 0
c p weight -1 3 0
c p weight 2 5 0
c p weight -2 7 0
p cnf 2 1
1 2 0
